subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Nikolay Davydenko of Russia defeated second-seeded Fernando Verdasco of Spain, 6-4, 7-5, to win the Malaysia Open in Kuala Lumpur.
